Description.206: A homeschooled teenager begins to suspect her mother is keeping a dark secret from her.
Description.207: Story revolves around a top-secret resort for retired U.S. intelligence officers.

Description.209: In the colorful future, a cab driver unwittingly becomes the central figure in the search for a legendary cosmic weapon to keep Evil and Mr. Zorg at bay.
Description.210: Violence and mayhem ensue after a hunter stumbles upon a drug deal gone wrong and more than two million dollars in cash near the Rio Grande.
Description.211: An undercover cop and a mole in the police attempt to identify each other while infiltrating an Irish gang in South Boston.
Description.212: A group of intergalactic criminals must pull together to stop a fanatical warrior with plans to purge the universe.
Description.213: Seventh entry in the long-running Mission: Impossible series.

Description.232: A group of high-end professional thieves start to feel the heat from the LAPD when they unknowingly leave a clue at their latest heist.

Description.235: An Interpol agent tracks the world's most wanted art thief.
Description.236: The drug-induced utopias of four Coney Island people are shattered when their addictions run deep.
